div.p: Knife handles, together with iron ornaments for the sheath, of all kinds, very beneficial for silversmiths or other artisans, made by Io: Theodori de Brÿ.
New knife covers along with fittings for sheaths, in various manners, very useful for goldsmiths and other lovers of art.
